{
  "stem": "5639.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And because he had a non-Jewish wife, that was one more reason why he went into hiding-- not to create a situation where she would be confronted with a choice, or with an order to abandon her husband, and so on.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they have a three-year-old daughter and for five-- for four years, the child did not know that her father is hiding in the attic.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Again, they did not want to expose her to a situation whether she might be accosted by a militia, by a French militia, by a raid of maquis who are looking constantly for food and for medications, if it would become known that there is a veterinary surgeon.",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he came down from the attic only at night.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And at the end of the war-- no, four years-- no, maybe it was three years or two years.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Whatever the length of time was, the child did not know that the father is with them.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I think it was also psychologically a very good move, because she didn't have a double standard.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She was not told to hide something, to deny something, to negate something.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that was it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "While we are still on subject of France, I want to tell you that out of my five uncles, all survived, all in hiding.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Except one.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, in southern France.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Except one, who stayed in Paris.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he was saved from the transport going from [NON-ENGLISH] by engine driver.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He taught-- he jumped the transport.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The engine driver gave him a sign to jump the transport.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He became level with the engine.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He opened the door to his cabin, dragged he in-- dragged him in-- and started to move the train down the railways, against the orders till the transport left.",
      "word_count": 29
    }
  ],
